{"tid":2272344,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"廚師掟鐵罐出馬路罪成 鄭紀航拒判罰款下令囚55天 斥公然挑戰法紀 惡行可能傷及途人","createTime":"2020-11-05T04:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T02:49:59.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"51b9dfd3bf294d21d9fd4639a26095981dafd1aa","tid":2272344,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"廚師被指去年11月「黎明行動」當天早上，在西灣河將銀色鐵罐掟出馬路，遭警員當場制服，事後被控阻街。案件經審訊後，裁判官鄭紀航今接納案中警長的證供，裁定被告罪成。鄭官更指此罪一般判處罰款，惟本案背景較過往案件有很大分別，因當日警方每次消除路面障礙後，便有人隨即再擲出垃圾及廢鐵等雜物，眾目睽睽下公然挑戰法紀，惡行可能傷及途人；而當天是上班上學日，被告等人沒有顧及大眾，行為對欲過正常生活的人造成極大不便，終判被告入獄55日。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/TMAQBDVFOFHCLCGOYRV7BPRG7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FTMAQBDVFOFHCLCGOYRV7BPRG7I%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4DUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=5d31115d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FTMAQBDVFOFHCLCGOYRV7BPRG7I%2F&h=3c50360d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/TMAQBDVFOFHCLCGOYRV7BPRG7I/</a>"},{"pid":"7f284e7498d3a211f27adecf8f891a224db1cfcf","tid":2272344,"uid":235015,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:16:55.000Z","msg":"高可晴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f75bfcdb42c9e552c32b216324774d7bc41ce68","tid":2272344,"uid":215611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:17:21.000Z","msg":"權表哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0753293bc4de0e27bdcba1e61d7e596322cb7a","tid":2272344,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:17:22.000Z","msg":"鄭官指，基於案情嚴重，須判阻嚇式刑罰，並且譴責被告惡行，判刑以兩個月換算為61日作起點，給予部份折扣後，總刑期為55天。鄭官判刑之餘，勸誡被告要洗心革面，認清是非黑白，務必要尊重法律，不可再犯法，並應消除成見，共建香港和諧社會。<br />\n<br />\n被告獲准以現金5,000元及母親人事現金5,000元保釋外出，等候上訴，其間須每晚10時至翌晨6時守宵禁令。"},{"pid":"4503e10ca3dfa4653abe8416d0ced4f9c434241d","tid":2272344,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:17:49.000Z","msg":"可能呢2個字都係大哂"},{"pid":"103efbac9cfd28511252983007606536f28717d1","tid":2272344,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"拘捕被告的警長張啟祥在辯方盤問下，承認當時只有一至兩秒時間觀察掟罐者正面，形容那刻是電光火石，而追捕時只憑衣着辨認誰是掟罐者<br />\n<br />\n鄭紀航信納案中警長張啟祥口供，認為他當日在現場從目擊被告掟罐、至展開追捕、到後來制服被告，全程均全神貫注、聚精會神，聚焦在被告身上，視線從未丟失，故裁定被告就是案發時擲罐的男子。"},{"pid":"a97ac769a8a41769b425dedcd70b621c28088586","tid":2272344,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ee59d003fbf256cc059e18d027ce58d126bb8a","tid":2272344,"uid":115579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:19:38.000Z","msg":"呢條官就係俾人登報斷絕關係果隻雜種"},{"pid":"a23d3ae85951d397d98d6e772fbceb17dcf71612","tid":2272344,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6c0897602939bea8a2199d0dd4b3edf033f97d","tid":2272344,"uid":199602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01ee59d003fbf256cc059e18d027ce58d126bb8a","tid":2272344,"uid":115579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:19:38.000Z","msg":"呢條官就係俾人登報斷絕關係果隻雜種"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:20:42.000Z","msg":"SOURCE??"},{"pid":"4b081df5bef25ee037af8d152ddfb12ac84d8681","tid":2272344,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T04:20:44.000Z","msg":"又係鄭紀航"},{"pid":"1eef65c5a